{"tid":365521,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人要傾心事","createTime":"2017-08-19T10:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T11:28:26.000Z","uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8d942ac0902598e2a61f6f6800f685f8cc743d","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:02:49.000Z","msg":"唔傾愛情類心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afde9c64c8dc538a4b4876382eb7e2bfc258a12","tid":365521,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:09:45.000Z","msg":"今日痾爛屎"},{"pid":"f05cb3cb1547aa909eeccd7e2f7b34976dba3bb6","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日痾爛屎</blockquote><br />\n非常好<br />\n痾爛屎，一爆出嚟果吓<br />\n成身鬆哂<br />\n普通痾屎比唔到咁爽快嘅感覺"},{"pid":"41c886f674dc9cd9c6464d8ab95a4e2d67e1e722","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"唔傾愛情就要比負評?<br />\n感情不等如愛情"},{"pid":"8c7ec94dfda82f4e61b4bfb688f2bb951df616ec","tid":365521,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:54:37.000Z","msg":"難得有唔係傾愛情既<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"e8ef3516ba2cac89dda664578d209d843ae0e80e","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>難得有唔係傾愛情既<br />\n支持</blockquote><br />\n多謝<br />\n有冇野想傾吓<br />\n例如今晚食咩餸好都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999043af57f84721310b9881d2149f04c12d05bd","tid":365521,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:58:22.000Z","msg":"連登好多Post ，但係無咩邊個post 想留言，點解"},{"pid":"c145b57a5bcae165e95d8cfd37a523cfdea7686f","tid":365521,"uid":9743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"生活係追求安穩定應該趁年青出外闖下?"},{"pid":"32f68ef05e25e7b7f6405f050c7eb6ec2ec69705","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登好多Post ，但係無咩邊個post 想留言，點解</blockquote><br />\n例如你呢一刻想搵有關於A嘅事<br />\n你只係見到有限嘅post<br />\n而即便係利用搜尋功能<br />\n下一刻你嘅需求可能已經改變<br />\n自然尋尋覓覓都冇咩POST想留言<br />\nTiming好重要"},{"pid":"5efffb8f48721d21cdc7cfee279c6fc2be0677f2","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生活係追求安穩定應該趁年青出外闖下?</blockquote><br />\n你係問安穩同冒險應該點揀<br />\n但當你提到安穩係要追求<br />\n其實你都係冒險<br />\n你呢刻坐起度咩都唔做，一樣係冒險<br />\n而你講到年青出去闖<br />\n已經暗示最後你都想要&quot;安穩&rdquo;<br />\n但安穩只係風險較低嘅冒險"},{"pid":"2ecda66d6c16c0eccee62eb831f32d2e8f0cbbe4","tid":365521,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:07:33.000Z","msg":"玩first impression 比人投係狗公同日日打飛機，代表咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔願做人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d19ef0d2e90409cc61951df1aaa872c5568a5fc","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩first impression 比人投係狗公同日日打飛機，代表咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔願做人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個bargaining power唔夠<br />\n比人投就覺得自己係<br />\n冇嚟志氣<br />\n你要做到你話佢係雞，佢一定係雞<br />\n你都可以投返佢係狗公，日日打j<br />\n狗婆/雞，日日捽碟<br />\n咁你係咪成日吠?"},{"pid":"2491c6fc5852befb15bb2321da990385f15ada4c","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a083ca562df8a6802005533670e2b68731ee05","tid":365521,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"愈大愈憎自己唔好個一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609bc76f268bc759c043bbbeecaf1d12dad8a001","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愈大愈憎自己唔好個一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊方面唔好?"},{"pid":"48871fbc88402fb30056d8ed6be5266a41ac5cca","tid":365521,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愈大愈憎自己唔好個一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊方面唔好?</blockquote><br />\n好多方面...<br />\n有時做人mean mean地<br />\n會自私<br />\n做野講野無諗清楚後果先做/講<br />\n又痴痴地線咁<br />\n對住朋友會交唔到個心出來<br />\n明明對方對自己係好<br />\n就不期然地會覺得人地想你衰<br />\n有時會覺得自己對身邊人好衰<br />\n對住屋企人既態度又係時好時差<br />\n心情一唔好既時候就好難控制到脾氣<br />\n<br />\n明明以前既自己唔係咁<br />\n但愈大愈憤世嫉俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d678762b0196e18c6be9b4c627e9307351acdc44","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>愈大愈憎自己唔好個一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊方面唔好?</blockquote><br />\n好多方面...<br />\n有時做人mean mean地<br />\n會自私<br />\n做野講野無諗清楚後果先做/講<br />\n又痴痴地線咁<br />\n對住朋友會交唔到個心出來<br />\n明明對方對自己係好<br />\n就不期然地會覺得人地想你衰<br />\n有時會覺得自己對身邊人好衰<br />\n對住屋企人既態度又係時好時差<br />\n心情一唔好既時候就好難控制到脾氣<br />\n<br />\n明明以前既自己唔係咁<br />\n但愈大愈憤世嫉俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁諗好正常<br />\n因為好人係唔一定有好報<br />\n如果我對人好同對人差，個預期回報係一樣<br />\n例如西口西臉<br />\n咁我冇必要花時間心機去做得好<br />\n而且你認為嘅好，起人地眼中可能係衰<br />\n咁為咗保護自己，不做不錯係上策<br />\n一係就寧我負天下人，莫讓天下人負我"},{"pid":"5fdd8c32246bd66882cbc4411283373989de8df5","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f480d1bd17ddd7cbeb19f00cc97b445b8cb64e63","tid":365521,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"咁點解要開係感情台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429e3f3b15df82bfc14bef783ddcb0bdacb4feeb","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T00:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點解要開係感情台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n感情不只等如愛情"},{"pid":"7ddf0f5400e8ebcfebcd7760722d7d0bc22f8dfc","tid":365521,"uid":35245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}